text: Ceroplesis intermedia is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1925. It is known from Tanzania and Kenya.BioLib.cz - Ceroplesis intermedia. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesis Category:Beetles described in 1925
